emains healthy, so I'll stay quiet."},{"type":"text","text":"Comparing current state (06:05 UTC) vs. last heartbeat (06:03 UTC):\n\n**Active sessions (same 3 cron sessions):**\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ running (this very instance)\n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ running (aborted in log but status=running — known/stale)\n- `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ running\n\n**Stable (no change):**\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` — idle, intact\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134` — completed normally ✅ (was completed at 05:56 UTC)\n- No new failures, no new sessions, no blockers surfaced\n\n**Pipeline: HEALTHY.** Nothing changed. Silent."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":30691,"output":605,"totalTokens":45673,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":433,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776233162935,"responseId":"062e5dcce9cd136a9258ef826b25e496","__openclaw":{"id":"0faabc98","seq":5}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"label":"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776233035984,"sessionId":"1ef31ea8-5d44-4196-83c3-72356bf36ede","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":40704,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776229649757,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/1ef31ea8-5d44-4196-83c3-72356bf36ede.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The memory returned no content (heartbeat-state.json is empty/disabled). Let me check the sessions_list results carefully to compare against the previous cycle.\n\n**Current active sessions (from sessions_list at 06:03 UTC):**\n\nRunning sessions:\n1. `cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611